\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0 It is near sunset. My father goes. he was an old and tired poet, it doesn\uc0{\u8217}t take long that it is Muhammad\uc0{\u8217}s turn to take him to a far away but close land in my dream. foot hot\uc0{\u8221} Mohammad was my young brother, left this world at the age of 24 by the accident)In me, a happy girl with innocent laughter turned off forever.}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0 It is evening, I\uc0{\u8217}m still stay in the after moon. migrated to another country to find that lost in me again: But the big part of me stay or left behind , in elementary school, art school and university that is full of stress and good or bad days. Every night I go back to those days with Muhammad and nothing else was born in me , expect missing and swallowing in the fact life is dying in living. like the other half of me\uc0{\u160} That Somewhere else with dead who travels to the old days,still goes to school with her fears and lives that dark prison. and the other half of me is living in a false reality that will be the scenario of my morbid dreams, in the evening.Is there a border between reality and mind? or just all of them are a picture of a dream, like a bubble in your hands!!}}\par
\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0 It is night, and in its black heart of night, my daughter was born. her eyes are similar to mine. Except of her, I have left behind others, even a part of my self. Being a long with her is most beautiful for me than any group. I am living with dualities and I like it because of myself is the face and Character of duality .Sometimes grumpy, hate and and or Sometimes smiling or love and other times beautiful or ugly..I\uc0{\u8217}m tired, It is coming dawn and my other half of me is on the way and waiting for me a sweet sleep.}}\par
